    Closed --> [*]

    note right of Unconnected
        Socket created without connection.
        connect() must be called before getInputStream/getOutputStream.
        bind() can be called once before connecting.
    end note

    note right of Connected
        Socket is connected.
        getInputStream() and getOutputStream() available.
        shutdownInput() or shutdownOutput() for half-close.
    end note

    note right of Closed
        Terminal state. Cannot reconnect or rebind.
        close() is idempotent.
        setOption/getOption throw IOException if closed.
    end note
